Create your own elegant, personalized invites using a unique DIY template that is simple to personalize. The original floral art by Raphaela Wilson features bright watercolor sunflowers and burgundy red roses with baby’s breath and greenery leaves for a soft botanical feel. Brown vintage barn wood lends for a rustic country touch, and mason jar string lights adds a beautiful sparkle. Not only is this invitation template ideal for rustic weddings, but with some creative rewording can also be perfect for a country birthday party, fall bridal shower, baby shower, or other special moments where sunflowers and red roses bring elegance to the decor. Should you customize the wild yellow daisy / sunflower themed design further, you can choose other wood colors, such as gray, navy blue, turquoise teal, burgundy, and ivory white. Even change the elegant white calligraphy script and modern fonts to a typography that best suits your fancy. Enjoy!
